<html>

<head>
    <title>Wild8.me | Restoran</title>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="~/images/favicon.png">
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/Content/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="~/Content/homepage.css" />
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <script src="~/Scripts/jquery-1.10.2.min.js"></script>
    <script src="~/Scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="~/Scripts/navbar_hide.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript">
        $(document).ready(function()
        {
            $('.carousel').carousel(
            {
                interval: 3250
            });

            $('.carousel').carousel('cycle');
        });
    </script>
</head>

<body>
    <!-- Carousel
    ================================================== -->
    <div id="wildCarousel" class="carousel slide">
        <!-- Indicators -->
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
            <li data-target="#wildCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
            <li data-target="#wildCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
            <li data-target="#wildCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div class="carousel-inner">
            <div class="item active">
                <img src="~/images/carousel_images/Wild8_interior.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h1>Wild8</h1>
                        <p>Najbolja jela s roštilja.</p>
                        <p>
                            <a class="btn btn-large btn-primary" href="#restaurant_info">Više informacija</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="~/images/carousel_images/Wild8_sample_food.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h1>Širok izbor</h1>
                        <p>Preko 100 različitih delikatesa.</p>
                        <p>
                            <a class="btn btn-large btn-primary" href="menu.html">Jelovnik</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="item">
                <img src="~/images/carousel_images/Wild8_delivery.jpg" class="img-responsive">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="carousel-caption">
                        <h1 style="text-color: black" class="header_special">Besplatna dostava</h1>
                        <p class="paragraph-special">Dostava pred vaša kućna vrata.</p>
                        <p>
                            <a class="btn btn-large btn-primary" href="contact_us.html">Posjetite nas</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Controls -->
        <a class="left carousel-control" href="#wildCarousel" data-slide="prev"><span class="icon-prev"></span></a>
        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#wildCarousel" data-slide="next"><span class="icon-next"></span></a>
    </div>
    <!-- /.carousel -->
    <!-- Marketing messaging and featurettes
    ================================================== -->
    <!-- Wrap the rest of the page in another container to center all the content. -->
    <div class="container marketing">
        <!-- Three columns of text below the carousel -->
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-circle" src="~/images/marketing_images/marketing_30min.jpg">
                <h2>Dostava u 30 min</h2>
                <p>Garantirana dostava unutar 30 minuta, inače ne plaćate narudžbu.</p>
                <p>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="#">Više »</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-circle" src="~/images/marketing_images/marketing_satisfaction.png">
                <h2>100% customer satisfaction</h2>
                <p>Rated 5/5 on every order.</p>
                <p>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="#">Više »</a>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
                <img class="img-circle" src="~/images/marketing_images/marketing_veggie.jpg">
                <h2>Vegeterijanski izbor</h2>
                <p>Ponuda vegeterijanskih jela s roštilja.</p>
                <p>
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="#">Više »</a>
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- /.row -->
        <!-- FEATURETTES -->
        <a name="restaurant_info"></a>
        <!-- anchor link for carousel button -->
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="featurette">
            <img class="featurette-image img-circle pull-right img-responsive" src="~/images/featurette_restaurant.jpg">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Restoran: <span class="text-muted">Wild8</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">
                Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Phasellus pulvinar faucibus neque, nec rhoncus nunc ultrices sit amet. Curabitur ac sagittis neque, vel egestas est. Aenean elementum, erat at aliquet hendrerit, elit nisl posuere tortor, id suscipit diam dui sed nisi. Morbi sollicitudin massa vel tortor consequat, eget semper nisl fringilla. Maecenas at hendrerit odio. Sed in mi eu quam suscipit bibendum quis at orci. Pellentesque fermentum nisl purus, et iaculis lectus pharetra sit amet.
            </p>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <div class="featurette">
            <img class="featurette-image img-circle pull-left img-responsive" src="~/images/owner.jpeg">
            <h2 class="featurette-heading">Vlasnik: <span class="text-muted">@Html.DisplayFor(model => model.OwnerName)</span></h2>
            <p class="lead">@Html.DisplayFor(model => model.OwnerHomepageInfo)</p>
        </div>
        <hr class="featurette-divider">
        <!-- /FEATURETTES -->
        <!-- FOOTER -->
        <footer>
            <p class="pull-right">
                <a href="#top">Idi na vrh</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                © Wild8 ugostiteljski obrt. · <a href="personnelLogin.html">Prijava osoblja</a>
            </p>
        </footer>
    </div>
    <!-- /.container -->
</body>

</html>
